  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">EC SWS Drought Response - SomRep2</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">SWS Emergency Drought Response Funding - WV Somalia, with DEC funding for the first 6 months of the project. &quot;Drought recovery and building resilience to natural disasters is a high priority in Somalia, especially now in 2017, that a severe drought is hitting the country. Households and communities must recover, adapt and diversify their livelihoods and asset base in order to cope effectively during both harsh dry seasons and disaster episodes. SomReP&#x2019;s approach acknowledges the need to recover from shock quickly and its programming seeks to promote the local absorptive and adaptive capacity of households and communities. While promoting drought recovery, the program also builds institutional capacity, strengthens the natural resource management that underpins resilience livelihood, and prevents loss of livelihood assets through proactive early action.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
